<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #374151;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #EC4899;
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #F9FAFB;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        border-top: none;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #EC4899;
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #DB2777;
      }
      .highlight {
        background-color: #FDF2F8;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid #EC4899;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">üéÅ Wishare</h1>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9;"><%= t('app.tagline') %></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2 style="color: #EC4899; margin-top: 0;"><%= t('invitations.show.title') %></h2>
        
        <p><%= t('emails.invitation.greeting') %> üëã</p>
        
        <p><%= t('emails.invitation.body', sender_name: @sender.display_name) %></p>
        
        <div class="highlight">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>What is Wishare?</strong></p>
          <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0;">Wishare is a platform where you can create and share wishlists with friends & family, making gift-giving easier and more thoughtful for any occasion.</p>
        </div>
        
        <% if @existing_user %>
          <p>Great news! You already have a Wishare account. Just click the button below to accept the invitation and start sharing wishlists:</p>
        <% else %>
          <p>To get started, you'll need to create a free Wishare account and accept the invitation:</p>
        <% end %>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a href="<%= @invitation_url %>" class="button"><%= t('emails.invitation.action') %></a>
        </div>
        
        <% unless @existing_user %>
          <p><small><strong>New to Wishare?</strong> Don't worry! Clicking the link above will guide you through creating your account first.</small></p>
        <% end %>
        
        <p>Once connected, you'll be able to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Create and organize your wishlists</li>
          <li>View their wishlists</li>
          <li>Mark items as purchased (hidden from them)</li>
          <li>Never run out of gift ideas again!</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Looking forward to seeing you on Wishare!</p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Best regards,<br>
The Wishare Team</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280;"><%= t('emails.invitation.footer') %></p>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280;">
          Can't click the button? Copy and paste this link: <br>
          <a href="<%= @invitation_url %>" style="color: #EC4899;"><%= @invitation_url %></a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>